e=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">年以上</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">java</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">相关经验；</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">1</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">年以上</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">Android</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">开发经验</span></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0\\\"><span style=\\\";font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\\\">2<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、精通</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">Android</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">开发平台及框架原理，能独立进行</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">Android</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">应用程序开发，精通</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">Android</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">的基本组件使用</span></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0\\\"><span style=\\\";font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\\\">3<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、熟悉</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">java</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">，熟悉常用设计模式，有个人独立开发完整产品经验者优先</span></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0\\\"><span style=\\\";font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\\\">4<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、熟练使用</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">Android</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">各种布局与控件，熟悉各种动画场景的运用</span></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0\\\"><span style=\\\";font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\\\">5<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、对移动领域新技术有较强的学习能力、独立解决问题的能力</span></span></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0\\\"><span style=\\\";font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\\\">6<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">、热爱互联网金融优先</span></span></p><p><br/></p>\')','0');
